ActSpecial Economic Measures Act
SubjectSpecial Economic Measures (Nicaragua) Permit Authorization Order
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister to issue to any individual or person in Canada and any Canadian outside Canada a permit to carry out a specified activity or transaction, or any class of activity or transaction that is otherwise restricted or prohibited pursuant to the Special Economic Measures (Nicaragua) Regulations.
